5) FULL JOIN: fetch all matching records from left side and right side 

-> in simple language we can say that full join combination of left and right join
-> in MYsql full join is not working
solution:
-> we can commbined left and right join result using UNION concept

-----------
union:
-> to commbined two tables without duplicate value we can use union 

